:h3.Hypertext Link
:p.You have moved horizontally via a hypertext link.
:p.You have :hp2.not:ehp2. moved vertically. This means a
:hp2.Cancel:ehp2. or :hp2.Exit:ehp2. command will exit the book and
return to the bookshelf.
